{"tid":2170489,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【電音撚】我第一首電音作品 Paradise　作曲真係唔易","createTime":"2020-08-23T10:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T16:37:32.000Z","uid":78806,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3e486bd99d589e6b4bcf4815be0742ce648e433d","tid":2170489,"uid":78806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZ7x_otQSZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBZ7x_otQSZI&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=a11ea2ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZ7x_otQSZI</a>"},{"pid":"4b52262bc90436e49366e0423c11586325aa5bfc","tid":2170489,"uid":78806,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"講少少創作感想<br />\n<br />\n由舊年開始跟一個英國tutor網上學編曲，學左一年<br />\n<br />\n由舊年9月開始構思melody，3月開始編曲，段段續續用差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為整首電音好易，但我可以好肯定講，難度大約等於GPA過3.5。<br />\n<br />\n1. 錢，無論Ableton、VST、所有軟件都係搶錢的，前前後後淨係買軟件用左3萬蚊。如果唔係當興趣，而係當正職真係食得屎。<br />\n<br />\n2. 識琴、吉他、鼓，真係缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n3. 無盡既耐性。整中間果段melody我諗我聽左起碼1000次。"},{"pid":"b5c279e34cd1525802e3bf6cb6adcd6aa57c40e6","tid":2170489,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"幾好聽，編得好豐富<br />\n不過麻麻地chorus/melody(?) 嗰隻樂器聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲太嘈太刺耳<br />\n利申唔識嘢，just 9 up"},{"pid":"85af1e241549520dab9bce6fb4a1fc0a437bb598","tid":2170489,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"Btw鍾意intro outro"},{"pid":"02a98c0ed6a6d8408bcc500c395e6a0d93529974","tid":2170489,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c279e34cd1525802e3bf6cb6adcd6aa57c40e6","tid":2170489,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"幾好聽，編得好豐富<br />\n不過麻麻地chorus/melody(?) 嗰隻樂器聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/